# Changelog


## [1.0.3] - 2025-09-09
### Added
- Color and typography controls for HTML fields, section headings, and list field column headings
- 50px spacing between adjacent textareas
- Default typography for Gravity Wiz Nested Forms elements

## [1.0.2] - 2025-09-08
### Added
- Typography and color controls for field descriptions
## FIxed
- Submit button styling not overriding Gravity Forms themes

## [1.0.1] - 2025-09-07
### Fixed
- Checkbox alignment issue on the left margin
- Hover state on buttons not working

## [1.0.0] - 2025-09-02
### Added
- Initial launch of plugin
